---
import HigthLight from "@atoms/HigthLight .astro";
---

<section class="flex flex-col gap-3 mt-11 md:mt-14">
  <h1
    class="name my-3 animate-move-bg font-semibold text-5xl md:text-6xl bg-clip-text bg-purple-600"
  >
    <span class="text-transparent">BYSERGR</span>
  </h1>
  <p class="text-gray-300">
    I'm <HigthLight>Software Engineer</HigthLight> with more than 3 years of
    experience building and maintaining complex systems, using agile
    methodologies, also different technologies and tools such as
    <HigthLight>Nodejs</HigthLight>,
    <HigthLight>Golang</HigthLight>,
    <HigthLight>SQL</HigthLight>,
    <HigthLight>MongoDB</HigthLight>,
    <HigthLight>Docker</HigthLight> among others, writing modern,
    high-performance and robust software.
  </p>
  <p class="text-gray-300">Do you want to hire my services as a Developer?</p>
  <p class="text-gray-300">
    Check my
    <a
      target="_blank"
      aria-label="Resume"
      rel="noopener"
      href="/RESUME.pdf"
      class="transition font-semibold text-white border-white border-b w-fit border-dashed"
      >RESUME</a
    >.
  </p>
</section>
